
This is like ANSYS, but open source: http://www.nic.funet.fi/pub/sci/physics/elmer/doc/ElmerguiManual.pdf

- input file
- model definitions
- utility functions
- solver input files
- solution and post processing

elmer software suite
importing finite element mesh files in various formats
generating finite element partitionings for geometry input files
setting up pde-systems to solve
exporting model data and results

can automatically call paraview

parallel solver: ElmerSolver_mpi
GUI hides a number of operations

dev package of Qt 4 installed

export ELMERGUI_HOME=/usr/local/bin
export PATH=$PATH:$ELMERGUI_HOME

mesh generators:
- ElmerGrid, built-in
- Tetgen, optional
- Netgen, built-in
